OOC: Let's just assume that Kenzo's already with Pacificus Maximals.
Kenzo heard her crying and gently lifted her up. 
"Little children shouldn't play outside by themselves."
He wispered in her ear.  He turned to take her back into the 
Pacificus Maximals base.

[Tag anyone in there]
